«c5»Wouldn't it be interesting to know how the charts looked like 5-6 years
ago, when the scene was at its best as so many claim? Wouldn't it be cool
to see if the «c2»same sceners and productions «c5»were also popular so many years
ago?«»
«»
In any case, this time «c2»D.I.S.C. «c5»presents some historical charts based on
the votes we received after issue 10, from Eastern 1995 till early 1996.
98% of the votes are taken from our paper votesheets, as I managed to loose
about all digital votes.«»
«»
«»
«c4»First Place give 4 points, Second Place 2 points and Third Place 1 point.«» 
